1225701.text: A report was just filed against me by a Caucasian lady who overheard me chopping it up with my fave (black) security guard. My friend, the guard, told me she'd been up for 72 hours. To which I replied, "Damn girl! You're lucky you aint in prison!" an allusion to the rich literature suggesting a lack of sleep impairs decision making and the ability to moderate one's emotions. Although that pales in comparison to the white lady in the Sazerac who called Barack Hussein Obama the n-word then asked to have me removed. So there's that
